Package: manipulateWidget
Type: Package
Title: Add Even More Interactivity to interactive charts
Version: 0.4.0
Date: 2017-01-04
Authors@R: c(
    person("Francois", "Guillem", , "francois.guillem@rte-france.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("RTE", role = "cph")
    )
Description: Like package 'manipulate' does for static graphics, this package
    helps to easily add controls like sliders, pickers, checkboxes, etc. to an
    interactive chart created with htmlWidget that can be used to
    modify the input data or the parameters of the chart.
Imports:
    shiny,
    miniUI,
    htmlwidgets
Suggests:
    dygraphs,
    leaflet,
    plotly,
    xts,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
